scenarioInformation.title: User Control and Freedom
scenarioInformation.description:
One of the key corner stones of user control and freedom is implementing methods for the user to control and back out of critical actions in software.

Neutron Financial, a bank, is currently looking to redesign their e-banking website. They have tasked you with coming up for the design of their account transfer tool. Remember to implement control over the transfer, and to provide a way for the user to escape from the action.
